  <summary date="2024-01-10T15:26:36Z" status="Introduced in House">Medal of Honor Act

This bill increases the monthly special pension for living Medal of Honor recipients from $1,619.34 to $8,333.33 and establishes a rate of $1,489.73 for the monthly special pension for surviving spouses of Medal of Honor recipients. Both amounts must be adjusted annually for inflation.</summary>
